Interface Target<TData>

  • Type Parameters:
    TData - The type of the value(s) this target represents.
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public Target<TData>

    A target output in a class Dataset.

    An interface is provided to cater for scenarios with differing output requirements (e.g. single vs multiple).
